query:
SELECT substr(event_date::VARCHAR, 0, 11) AS "EventDate",
       sms_type AS sms_type,
       anc_id AS anc_id,
       age AS age,
       health_worker_location_name AS health_worker_location_name,
       health_worker_name AS health_worker_name,
       height AS height,
       weight AS weight,
       previous_risks AS previous_risks,
       lmp_edd AS lmp_edd,
       parity AS parity,
       gravidity AS gravidity,
       message AS message,
       event_date AS event_date,
       intervention AS intervention,
       breastfeeding AS breastfeeding,
       client_type AS client_type,
       gender AS gender,
       child_no AS child_no,
       first_name AS first_name,
       second_name AS second_name,
       third_name AS third_name,
       last_name AS last_name,
       date_of_birth AS date_of_birth,
       year_of_birth AS year_of_birth,
       patient_contact AS patient_contact,
       location_id AS location_id,
       contact AS contact,
       anc_visit_date AS anc_visit_date,
       next_anc_date AS next_anc_date,
       event_id AS event_id,
       symptoms AS symptoms,
       status AS status,
       location AS location,
                   supplements AS supplements,
                   micronutrients AS micronutrients,
                   health_insurance_id AS health_insurance_id,
                   appointment_status AS appointment_status,
                   muac_status AS muac_status,
                   response_status AS response_status,
                   risk_level AS risk_level,
                   bmi AS bmi,
                   muac AS muac,
                   lmp AS lmp,
                   bp AS bp,
                   mother_symptoms AS mother_symptoms,
                   ethnicity AS ethnicity,
                   household AS household,
                   toilet AS toilet,
                   handwashing AS handwashing,
                   planned_delivery_location AS planned_delivery_location,
                   death_date AS death_date,
                   location_of_death AS location_of_death,
                   death_code AS death_code,
                   logface_risk AS logface_risk,
                   death_reason AS death_reason,
                   child_symptoms AS child_symptoms,
                   delivery_location AS delivery_location,
                   delivery_method AS delivery_method,
                   child_risk_level AS child_risk_level,
                   health_worker_contact AS health_worker_contact,
                   team AS team,
                   weight_z_score AS weight_z_score,
                   height_z_score AS height_z_score,
                   nutrition_status AS nutrition_status,
                   growth_status AS growth_status,
                   feeding_category AS feeding_category
FROM events_details
ORDER BY "EventDate" DESC
LIMIT 10000;
